content.text: Hey there how is your day going?
Great so far! I'm about to graduate high school next week and I'm really excited for what the future holds.
That's awesome! I'm sure you'll do great things. What are you planning on doing after high school?
I'm not 100% sure yet but I'm thinking about going to college. What about you?
I'm in college right now studying business. I'm really enjoying it so far.
That's awesome! I've always thought about going into business but I'm not sure if I'm cut out for it.
It's definitely not for everyone but if you're interested in it I would definitely recommend looking into it.
I will! Thanks for the advice.
No problem!
I'm also looking forward to starting a new life in a new state with my dog.
That sounds exciting! What state are you moving to?
I'm moving to Oregon! I'm really excited to explore a new place and meet new people.
That's great! I've heard Oregon is beautiful. I'm sure you'll love it there.
Thanks! I'm sure I will too.
What do you like to do for fun?
I love to cosplay! I've been doing it for years and it's my favorite hobby.
That's awesome! I've never cosplayed before but I've always thought it looked like a lot of fun.
It is! It's a great way to express your creativity and meet new people.
I can see why you love it!
Yeah it's the best
